'''Headstrong Games''' is the London-based studio of [[wikipedia:Kuju Entertainment|Kuju Entertainment]], specialized in [[wikipedia:Wii|Wii]]-games. As such, they produced the Wii version of ''[[The Lord of the Rings: Aragorn's Quest]]''.
